Package: ota
Type: Package
Title: Online Teaching Allocation Roster Management
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Januar", "Harianto",
      email = "januar.harianto@sydney.edu.au",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: An R package for managing Online Teaching Allocation (OTA) rosters 
    at the University of Sydney. Provides functions to load roster data from Excel, 
    create timestamped snapshots, compare versions to track changes, and generate 
    formatted reports with paycode management. Supports multiple teaching units and 
    automatically identifies additions, removals, replacements, and role changes.
